WEBVTT

00:09.735 --> 00:13.011
(Man) Good evening.
Good evening, good evening.

00:13.135 --> 00:14.693
Hello, chaps.

00:14.815 --> 00:16.612
(Orchestra tuning up)

00:17.855 --> 00:19.732
Thank you for coming.

00:20.935 --> 00:25.531
Now then, we have a long way to go,
so... er... keep your powder dry.

00:25.655 --> 00:26.929
(Chuckling)

00:27.055 --> 00:30.007
Righty-ho...
settle down, now.

00:30.095 --> 00:31.608
(Taps baton)

00:34.335 --> 00:36.769
1... 2... 3...

00:36.895 --> 00:44.324
(Woman) # I'm mad about the boy

00:45.455 --> 00:51.132
# I know it's stupid to be
mad about the boy

00:52.775 --> 00:57.087
# I'm so ashamed of it,
but must admit

00:57.215 --> 01:03.893
# The sleepless nights
I've had about the boy

01:06.935 --> 01:10.564
# On the silver screen

01:10.695 --> 01:16.486
# He melts my foolish heart
in every single scene

01:18.535 --> 01:21.208
# Although I'm quite aware

01:21.335 --> 01:29.367
# That here and there are traces...
of the cad about the boy

01:32.735 --> 01:37.445
# And Lord knows, I'm not a fool girl

01:39.335 --> 01:43.965
# I really shouldn't care

01:45.975 --> 01:49.604
# Lord knows, I'm not a schoolgirl

01:49.735 --> 01:56.493
# In the flurry of her first affair

01:58.095 --> 02:07.128
# Will it ever cloy, this odd diversity
of misery and joy?

02:08.935 --> 02:13.611
# I'm feeling quite insane
and young again

02:13.735 --> 02:20.732
# And all because I'm mad
about the boy

